      "factorStandard": "ASME-VV40-2018",
      "requiredLevel": 2,
      "achievedLevel": 2,
      "factorStatus": "assessed",
      "acceptanceCriteria": "Independent analyst review of boundary conditions, material assignments, and load application; documented checklist completed.",
      "rationale": "Independent review by second analyst at each participating organization confirmed boundary condition application (fixed block base, load applied at superior block centroid), material property assignments, and contact definitions. Checklist archived in project records."
