      "acceptanceCriteria": "Validation scenario (ASTM F1717 bench test) is representative of the intended regulatory submission context; device, loading, and geometry match COU.",
      "rationale": "Validation performed on production-equivalent non-cannulated 7.5 mm pedicle screws under the identical ASTM F1717 protocol referenced in the regulatory COU. Two independent laboratories provide cross-validation. The validation scenario is directly representative of the intended use context for the 510(k) submission."
    }
