    "actor": "https://uofa.net/synth/actor/fda-cdrh-osel-credibility-team",
    "role": "Credibility assessment team",
    "outcome": "Accepted",
    "rationale": "12 of 13 V&V 40 credibility factors meet or exceed required levels. The single shortfall (Test conditions, achieved 1 vs. required 2) is accepted because the COU is explicitly scoped to static compression-bending per ASTM F1717 and the regulatory decision does not require multi-condition validation at this stage. All three QoIs satisfy quantitative acceptance criteria (E/uval <1.96, %diff <10%) across N=11 specimens and two independent laboratories. Overall credibility is sufficient to support a Medium model risk level decision.",
